      },
      "date": "2013-01-23 04:52:29.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/a8330c0e-6516-11e2-804e-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
